## Example 1: Forge Modules Only

**Puppetfile:**
```ruby
# Core dependencies
mod 'puppetlabs-stdlib', '9.7.0'
mod 'puppetlabs-concat', '9.0.2'
mod 'puppetlabs-firewall', '8.1.3'
```

**Dependencies directory:** `/tmp/project/migration-dependencies/`
```
/tmp/project/migration-dependencies/
├── stdlib/
├── concat/
└── firewall/
```

**Expected output:**
{% raw %}
```json
{
  "dependencies": [
    {
      "name": "puppetlabs-stdlib",
